text: Iranotricha is a genus of ground spiders containing the single species, Iranotricha lutensis. It was first described by Alireza Zamani, M. Seiedy, A. Saboori & Yuri M. Marusik in 2018, and is only found in Iran. ==References== ==External links== Category:Gnaphosidae Category:Monotypic Araneomorphae genera
title: Iranotricha
